ITC Share Price vis-à-vis S&P CNX Nifty <:: chart: A line chart titled "ITC Share Price vis-à-vis S&P CNX Nifty" displays two lines over time. The x-axis represents months from Apr-08 to Mar-09. The left y-axis is labeled "ITC Share Price (Rs.)" with values ranging from 100 to 250. The right y-axis is labeled "S&P CNX Nifty" with values ranging from 2000 to 6000. The legend indicates that a thick black line represents "ITC Share Price" and a grey dotted line represents "S&P CNX Nifty". Both lines show a general downward trend from Apr-08 to Oct-08, followed by a slight recovery or stabilization towards Mar-09. The ITC Share Price line shows less severe fluctuations compared to the S&P CNX Nifty line. ::> Note – Indicates monthly closing positions. During the financial year ended 31st March, 2009, the Company's Shares have outperformed the market; while the S&P CNX Nifty has fallen by 36%, the decline in the Company's Share price was only 10%. ITC Share Price & Volume traded on NSE <::Line chart titled "ITC Share Price & Volume traded on NSE" showing three data series over time from April 2008 to March 2009. The x-axis represents months from Apr-08 to Mar-09. There are two y-axes: the left y-axis is "ITC Share Price (Rs.)" ranging from 100 to 250, and the right y-axis is "Volume Traded ('000 Shares)" ranging from 50,000 to 250,000. The three data series are: 1. **Highest (thick black line)**: Represents the monthly highest share price. It starts around 215 in Apr-08, peaks at approximately 225 in May-08, then generally declines to about 180 in Nov-08, and fluctuates between 185 and 190 until Mar-09. 2. **Lowest (dotted black line)**: Represents the monthly lowest share price. It starts around 200 in Apr-08, declines to 160 in Jul-08, rises to 180 in Aug-08, drops sharply to 130 in Oct-08, then recovers to 175 in Feb-09, and drops to 140 in Mar-09. 3. **Volume Traded (light gray dotted line)**: Represents the monthly volume traded in thousands of shares. It starts around 125,000 in Apr-08, rises to 160,000 in Jul-08, drops to 75,000 in Aug-08, peaks at 200,000 in Oct-08, then generally declines to 60,000 in Feb-09, and rises to 100,000 in Mar-09. Legend: Highest, Lowest, Volume Traded. : chart::> Note – Indicates monthly high & low price and monthly volume.
